{"tid":195521,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"會唔會為咗一個人而避開所有嘢","createTime":"2017-04-10T16:04:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T01:50:10.000Z","uid":37804,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e5c85d3fa2d6f7bad769d755605788921b73b256","tid":195521,"uid":37804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T16:04:02.000Z","msg":"唔想突然又諗起一個人，所以會避開共同相識嘅人，怕會從任何人口中聽到佢嗰名或者消息。<br />\n<br />\n同佢去過嘅地方，搭車前嘅一段路，一齊去過嘅餐廳都唔敢再去。<br />\n<br />\n見到佢鐘意嘅食物，鐘意嘅顏色，鐘意嘅說話，所有所有嘢都令我好想避開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"919b94a3c4cd4eebe690bc02f1b6ccf500d5663f","tid":195521,"uid":46093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T16:12:00.000Z","msg":"唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c2a60f380a4070edf0687d8455092de7620080f","tid":195521,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T16:13:12.000Z","msg":"避咩呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你根本避唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d503b3e996423f526e93fc0977099f9de87a188","tid":195521,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T16:13:34.000Z","msg":"會<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"344513d70b4c0a52458acdb7464bd3339705463c","tid":195521,"uid":13873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T18:00:44.000Z","msg":"會<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會好唔想聽到朋友口中提起佢"},{"pid":"4a791563bfd6322114541be5b9b37bb613ccc302","tid":195521,"uid":84595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T19:46:05.000Z","msg":"會，避到攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n避係無用，由佢唔開心，差唔多時候痛夠就要醒"},{"pid":"68d1766f91e5f9eda882fbe21bac08907100486b","tid":195521,"uid":68661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T21:24:59.000Z","msg":"會 但都係會日日諗住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b761fed37abef0a0ab1b46972ae575550c8790e","tid":195521,"uid":37804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T01:50:10.000Z","msg":"點樣避都好，佢始終都係你心中，慢慢接受慢慢放低囉"}]}